amazon_data.title: OCUBE LED Digital Alarm Clock with 5 Optional Alarm Sounds, USB Charging Port, Full-Range Brightness Dimmer, Big White Digit Display, Snooze, Adjustable Alarm Volume, Mains Powered
features: Mains Powered and Battery Backup: Come with a 3 Prong plug that will go into your wall socket to power the clock, and you have the option to back up the time and alarm settings with 3 AAA batteries (NOT included) in case of power outage. During use of the backup battery, the screen will go blank and the alarm will not sound.
amazon_data.description: Product Description In pursuit of waking up in the morning feeling refreshed, you need an ideal alarm clock. This Digital Alarm Clock by OCUBE has 5 selectable alarm sounds, is easy-to-read regardless of distance or visual acuity thanks to its 4.6" large LED display. The clock also has an adjustable alarm volume and a USB output for mobile charging. This stylish, compact and minimalist digital clock goes with any decor. It is perfect for home, bedroom, kitchen, hotel, office, nightstand, table, desk, shelf, guest room, TV room. USB port for charging your devices Start your day with a fully-charged device. This simple alarm clock offers an integrated USB port that charges your phones, tablets, or other 5V electronics. 9 Minute Snooze Function This clock has a large snooze button that you can easily find when you're groggy. The snooze allows the alarm to sound every 9 minutes until it is turned off.It is very suitable for those mornings when you need some extra Zzzz’s. Tips: the alarm sound will last for 8 minutes unless interrupted by pressing any buttons. 12/24-Hour Display The time can be set to show in 12-hour or 24-hour (military time). Just short press the "12/24HR" button to toggle between 12 and 24-hour as your reading habits. PM icon will display when time reaches to afternoon if 12H format selected.
